graph TD
    Input[Tool Call Request] --> Queue[Tool Call Queue]
    
    Queue --> Seq{Sequential Execution}
    Seq --> ToolCall[Next Tool Call]
    
    ToolCall --> Validate[Tool Validator]
    Validate --> Valid{Valid?}
    
    Valid -->|No| ValError[Validation Error]
    ValError --> Recovery
    
    Valid -->|Yes| Execute[Execute via MCP]
    Execute --> Timeout{Timeout Check}
    
    Timeout -->|Exceeded| TimeoutError[Timeout Error]
    TimeoutError --> Recovery
    
    Timeout -->|OK| Result[Process Result]
    Result --> Success{Success?}
    
    Success -->|No| Recovery[Error Recovery Engine]
    Recovery --> Severity[Classify Severity]
    Severity --> Strategy[Choose Strategy]
    Strategy --> Retry{Can Retry?}
    
    Retry -->|Yes| RetryCount{Attempts < Max?}
    RetryCount -->|Yes| Execute
    RetryCount -->|No| Fail[Mark Failed]
    
    Retry -->|No| Fail
    Success -->|Yes| UpdateState[Update System State]
    
    UpdateState --> Context[Update Context Cache]
    Context --> History[Add to History]
    History --> More{More Tools?}
    
    More -->|Yes| Seq
    More -->|No| Complete[Return Results]
    
    Fail --> More
    
    style Execute fill:#2196f3
    style Recovery fill:#ff9800
    style Complete fill:#4caf50
    style Fail fill:#f44336
